{"tid":1180432,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得寵物小精靈好野蠻","createTime":"2019-05-31T23:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T04:54:41.000Z","uid":98692,"like":33,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2feedfe09ab26ecac1b9e6021575c8405a05b977","tid":1180432,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:07:35.000Z","msg":"一日到黑就打算捉人翻去做寵物，明明喺野外生活得好地地，結果就用精靈球困住佢。<br />\n如果人地唔想被捉，就直接派隻噴火龍去打佢，打到暈左就再困住佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58810b5a76d0f0041628d270e81fc3bf5a9369e2","tid":1180432,"uid":120715,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:46:23.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n所以小智肯俾比卡超唔返入去精靈球<br />\n算係幾人道<br />\n仲有火箭兵團隻喵喵怪"},{"pid":"710fa4d039262e87d5c7a27f0b38ad3ddc055add","tid":1180432,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"人地個世界個結構同生物間關係係咁<br />\n你用現實世界個套去睇另一個世界？"},{"pid":"0fc5427b217a1db78c31515fde749f4ae95935c9","tid":1180432,"uid":234509,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:11:00.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n動保撚幾時反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad928503594be5cb727bd88fb561760383d3b18","tid":1180432,"uid":34243,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:13:47.000Z","msg":"仲要無限配種 生得唔靚唔夠能力就放生 年中幾百萬隻精靈一出世就回歸大自然老母都見唔到(雖然老母好大機會都係百變怪)<br />\n<br />\n能力高都未必好彩 好多時都係要係電腦入面住一世 真正陪到主人既精靈就得個6隻"},{"pid":"8464d29fa5b24b7986dd95911cda480c4ee44e20","tid":1180432,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"Be car be car<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924ca5166f842ea4dd